description:
The investment seeks to track the performance of a benchmark index that measures the investment return of large-capitalization growth stocks in the United States.
 The fund employs an indexing investment approach designed to track the performance of the S&P 500® Growth Index, which represents the growth companies, as determined by the index sponsor, of the S&P 500 Index. The index measures the performance of large-capitalization growth stocks in the United States.
